 src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n當買盤熱刺果場都係買般尼盤啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點樣有得贏呀</blockquote><br />\n佢自己寫曼聯熱刺李城<br />\n咁咪曼聯*熱刺*李城<br />\n如果買般尼盤<br />\n應該寫曼聯般尼李城<br />\n我理解錯誤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n霉西出既毒水係熱刺全場和<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我點知佢出咩水<br />\n上邊都沒寫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"696ecd1cd262a5523a74478dc6e8a47394dbc34f","tid":183102,"uid":6044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T19:14:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>以後係到出水</blockquote><br />\n你係邊個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你多左粒墨(.)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43e5866a14459446bbe632c1582544f8ef7e80f6","tid":183102,"uid":80080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T19:17:06.000Z","msg":"屌你老母呀！對乜撚野家呀！場場中使撚賭呀柒頭！屌柒你個撚樣死前床上痛苦十年！掛尿袋插胃喉！"},{"pid":"3ce1306d7cab0cd03ea5116f4c0bb19aaede5019","tid":183102,"uid":14872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T19:26:26.000Z","msg":"以後唔用Group？"},{"pid":"168570f48e19d99b52d9eba116cfdd9c53ca38ea","tid":183102,"uid":80080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T19:28:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>以後唔用Group？</blockquote><br />\n唔用group"},{"pid":"0fec20da063b3a8f91f43fe4ee8d2172b6da7969","tid":183102,"uid":89423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T19:29:49.000Z","msg":"其實100%中又使咩賭，輸屌贏要，欠左你嘅咩，宜家啲人真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7d1738826d4e9f5d689503375af00763a856cab","